{"tid":2054261,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"又話犯法一定要拉？64幾十萬人犯法林鄭點回應？","createTime":"2020-06-07T04:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-07T07:41:19.000Z","uid":175623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c04e065c27b7a59c302291ee337815a90cbf82b7","tid":2054261,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"唔該搵記者問下林鄭<br />\n<br />\n64就係一個最好事例證明 支那 林鄭 黑警係冇牙老虎 <br />\n證明咗你個句犯法一定要拉就係廢話！<br />\n<br />\n你由二月至六月開咗幾十萬張限聚令2000告票，以為就咁就可以嚇怕香港人唔示威集會？<br />\n<br />\n64當晚都係有幾十萬人上街 集會。<br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢黨歌法 黨安法？夠造埋呢！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">和理合流 天下無敵<br />\n係時候和理非上場啦！</span></span>"},{"pid":"98366f621486940eb1ace423b0ce51c1b811f0d3","tid":2054261,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"諗多左 果日好明顯係驚美國先唔敢郁"},{"pid":"e275d0c86593b624624cd2f204d8689e73d92332","tid":2054261,"uid":284429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T04:45:19.000Z","msg":"係證明和平與否係由黑警控制"},{"pid":"ee1dc4f27a2882db4bd6ed4099ed0f79e16016e7","tid":2054261,"uid":314731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T04:48:27.000Z","msg":"算啦<br />\n我對香港嘅記者都無乜希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a585ba9f7e4a78292aefbc9b0de8260e8419596","tid":2054261,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"98366f621486940eb1ace423b0ce51c1b811f0d3","tid":2054261,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T04:35:49.000Z","msg":"諗多左 果日好明顯係驚美國先唔敢郁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T07:40:29.000Z","msg":"姐係驚啦"},{"pid":"42c6982399b41108fc240242f72c8da154a57c60","tid":2054261,"uid":175623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e275d0c86593b624624cd2f204d8689e73d92332","tid":2054261,"uid":284429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T04:45:19.000Z","msg":"係證明和平與否係由黑警控制"},"citedBy":0,"rep